)

    FILTER(
        SUMMARIZE(
            'Sales Items',
            'Sales Items'[Document Sales Document VBELN],
            'Sales Items'[BILLING_DOCUMENT_VBELN],
            "Max Date", MAX('Sales Items'[Schedule Actual Goods Issue Date WADAT])

        'Sales Items'[Sales Items Sales Document Category VBTYP] = "C"
    ),
    [Max Date]
)
